Package: DTAimproved
Type: Package
Title: Improved Methods for Diagnostic Test Accuracy Meta-Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("DTA", "Researcher",
           email = "researcher@example.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Improved meta-analysis methods for diagnostic test accuracy studies
    based on comprehensive evaluation of existing methods. Includes adaptive
    method selection, robust estimators for sparse data, and ensemble methods.
    These methods address key flaws identified in standard approaches including
    Moses-Littenberg bias, sparse data handling, and convergence issues.
